-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:900,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:959}"><font color="#000000">Die Mission eines Mannes, Reinigung neu zu denken</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659535" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659535" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:312,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:312,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Es war ein Samstag im April, als Matthis Eberhardt auf seiner Terrasse in Offenburg stand und sich ärgerte.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Die Steinplatten waren grün vor Moos. Zwischen den Fugen wucherte Unkraut. Der alte Hochdruckreiniger stand in der Garage — 14 Kilo schwer, ein Kabel das nie lang genug war, und jedes Mal 20 Minuten Aufbau, bevor überhaupt ein Tropfen Wasser kam.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">„An dem Tag habe ich zum Gartenschlauch gegriffen", erinnert sich Eberhardt. <i>„Und wie jedes Mal: viel Wasser, kaum Druck, null Ergebnis."</i></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Da war der Moment, in dem die Idee entstand.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Nicht für ein besseres Gerät. Sondern für eine komplett andere Lösung.</span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:990,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:72,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1049}"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1302,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;a