ot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1361}"><font color="#000000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1302,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1361}"></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659450" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659450" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1312,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:22,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1371}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1312,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:22,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1371}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/fe15cb20-fd0c-43ec-b99b-7ad8c0787261/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/NEW%20ADVERTORIAL%20_34_.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1000" height="600" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:397,&quot;y&quot;:1334,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:0,&quot;abs_x&quot;:686,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1393}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496146943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496146943" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1364,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1423}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1364,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1423}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1364,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1423}"><font color="#000000">Was, wenn der Schlauch selbst genug Druck liefern könnte?</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659468" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659468" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:360,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:360,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}">Matthis Eberhardt ist Maschinenbauingenieur. Seit über 15 Jahren beschäftigt er sich mit Wassertechnik und Strömungsmechanik. Er wusste: In jedem Gartenschlauch steckt mehr Druck als die meisten ahnen.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}">Das Problem ist nicht der Schlauch. Es ist die Düse.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}">Herkömmliche Aufsätze verteilen das Wasser breit — der Druck geht verloren. Was fehlt, ist ein System, das den vorhandenen Wasserdruck bündelt und verstärkt.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}">Genau das hat Eberhardt konstruiert: Einen kompakten Aufsatz, der den Druck eines normalen Gartenschlauchs vervielfacht — ohne Motor, ohne Strom, ohne komplizierte Technik.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1444,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1503}">Die Idee war simpel. Die Umsetzung brauchte 18 Monate.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659432" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659432" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1824,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1883}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1824,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1883}"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/493082890342809234_3000x3000.webp?v=1776507012" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="500" natural-height="281" width="500" height="281" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:1824,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1883}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496247194" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496247194" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2275,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2334}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2275,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2334}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2275,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:34,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2334}"><font color="#000000">Vom Prototyp zum Bestseller</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659396" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659396" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:216,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:216,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}">Eberhardt baute den ersten Prototyp in seiner Werkstatt im Schwarzwald. Er testete ihn auf seiner eigenen Terrasse, auf der Einfahrt, auf Gartenmöbeln. Dann bei Nachbarn. Dann bei Freunden.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}">Das Feedback war jedes Mal dasselbe: „Warum gibt es das nicht schon längst?"</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}">Er nahm das Konzept zu mehreren Herstellern. Die Reaktion? Zurückhaltung. Ein Produkt ohne Motor, ohne Verschleißteile, ohne teures Zubehör — das passte nicht ins Sortiment.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}">Also ging Eberhardt seinen eigenen Weg. Gründung. Produktion. Direktvertrieb.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><strong>Das </strong><strong>Ergebnis</strong>: Turbowasher — der Aufsatz, der jeden Gartenschlauch in ein Hochdruck-Reinigungssystem verwandelt.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2320,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:24,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2379}">Heute ist er ein Bestseller in Deutschland, Österreich und der Schweiz.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659464" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026659464" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2556,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2615}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2556,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2615}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/1a433cb5-9810-4a6e-94ef-5426f77c8e4c/Untitleddesign4-ezgif.com-optimize.gif" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="600" natural-height="316" width="600" height="316" loading="lazy" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2556,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2615}"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1749496308373" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1749496308373" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3008,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3067}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3008,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3067}"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3008,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:69,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3067}"><font color="#000000">Warum es funktioniert</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026659434" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026659434" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:168,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:168,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}">Turbowasher nutzt ein Präzisions-Düsensystem, das den vorhandenen Wasserdruck deines Gartenschlauchs bündelt und gezielt verstärkt.&nbsp;</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}">Kein Motor. Kein Strom. Keine beweglichen Teile.&nbsp;</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}">Einfach auf den Gartenschlauch schrauben — und los. Aber wie kann ein kleiner Aufsatz so viel Druck erzeugen?</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"><br></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}">Das Prinzip ist simpel: Ein normaler Gartenschlauch liefert mehr Druck als die meisten denken. Das Problem sind herkömmliche Aufsätze — sie verteilen das Wasser breit, der Druck geht verloren. Turbowasher macht das Gegenteil: Er bündelt den Wasserstrahl durch ein Doppeldüsen-System so gezielt, dass die Reinigungskraft um ein Vielfaches steigt.</p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"></p><p bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:3087,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:48,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3146}"></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1776508652218" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1776508652218" data-resolution="3000x3000" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2556,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2615}"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc="" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:-2,&quot;y&quot;:2556,&quot;w&quot;:800,&quot;h&quot;:421,&quot;abs_x&quot;:287,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2615}"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/73babc52-852a-40b4-bf31-2e96d9de3bc7/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/ChatGPT%20Image%20